Package com.hemebiotech.analytics

Class SymptomFrequencyCounter

java.lang.Object
com.hemebiotech.analytics.SymptomFrequencyCounter
public class SymptomFrequencyCounter
extends java.lang.Object
Parameter given is a list of strings (symptoms), may contain duplicates Creates a set of string from initial list containing once every symptom retrieved: no duplicates. Counts the number of duplicates in the list for every symptom of the set The return object is a map associating symptoms and duplicate count.
